<lb n="7"/>middhelkuṁnnu dēvara vupahārā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ggēṭi polānanu jagannā 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>dha Ōjala cētanu konnakṣētraṁ 
<lb n="10"/><unclear>re</unclear>ṁḍu vuṭla valnaṁ buṭṭeṁḍukṣē 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>tramunnuppapuna gōśila gōtra 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>mu liṁgaṁ<unclear>na</unclear>śeṭṭi tama tallitaṁḍriki mē 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>namāmaku puṇyamugānu sama 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>¨rpiṁcenu maṁgaḷamahā śrī 
